Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.92,0:01:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}現在開始我將要充分享受你的悲鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.92,0:01:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}模擬 開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.95,0:01:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}第二十六號機構 貫式閉鎖態 鐵處女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.78,0:01:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}禍動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.00,0:02:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}第八號機構 碎式圓環態 法蘭克王國車輪刑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.47,0:02:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}禍動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.05,0:02:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}沒錯 這正是我期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.25,0:02:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}來吧 發出愉快的悲鳴倒下吧 婊子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.68,0:02:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}關於謳歌悲鳴的方法 你和我有數百年的差距
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.00,0:02:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}哭喊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.74,0:03:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}第三號機構 斷式落下態 斷頭台
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}菲雅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}婊子 婊子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.87,0:03:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}竟敢 竟敢這麼凌辱我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}婊子 婊子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.79,0:03:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}殺了你 滅了你 宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.23,0:04:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那是什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.95,0:04:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}總之得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.44,0:04:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}法蘭克王國的車輪刑 禍動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}悲鳴 想要聽悲鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.88,0:04:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我就是為此而被製造出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我就是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}回復正常吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}已經結束了 敵人已經跑了 菲雅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}到底在 幹什麼啊 你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}菲雅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.25,0:04:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}淋雨 這也是第一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}原來 是這麼冰冷的東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你想了解的我的真相 就是這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}春亮 她說的話全都是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.78,0:05:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我殺了好幾百人 只為殺戮而被製造出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.54,0:05:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以才被詛咒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.54,0:05:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}並且更諷刺的是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因為受到詛咒而獲得的人的意識
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}學會了罪孽這一概念
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}隨處可見的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}哼 也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我的詛咒只是隨處可見的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.43,0:05:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一定會讓持有者瘋狂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.84,0:05:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而變得不停使用我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}沒錯 隨處可見的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以說 我不會受到那詛咒的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只要留在這就沒問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.03,0:06:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我 從理解到了最根本的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.45,0:06:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我只是盲目地追尋著夢想和希望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}愚蠢到不作任何思考
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一味地想要忘記而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.72,0:06:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那種事根本不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.43,0:06:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}菲雅 冷靜點 你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我身負罪孽 殺人 殺人無數的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以才會被罪孽詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.04,0:06:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以 懲罰 懲罰是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}吶 我 真的可以被原諒嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}回去吧 這裡太冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你的回答真溫柔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.09,0:07:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}最差勁的溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}果然我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.14,0:07:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}等等菲雅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.73,0:07:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}菲雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.26,0:07:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}沒事嗎？春亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}春亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}菲雅 菲雅 等等 菲雅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.39,0:07:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}菲雅 菲雅 菲雅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.09,0:07:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}還不能起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}雖然做了緊急處理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}血…流了好多血
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}沒事的 有好好避開要害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}可能沒想像中的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:07:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是 命令式的提案
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}去醫院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.03,0:08:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你想說不要去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.90,0:08:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這樣的話 想怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.27,0:08:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}會生氣的 就算是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,0:08:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}追上那孩子 你要怎辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.23,0:08:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他以自己的意識離開的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而且 那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.95,0:08:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}雖然失去了手臂 但還沒放棄的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.14,0:08:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我覺得逃走也是好方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.62,0:08:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.26,0:08:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那傢伙一個人沉睡會比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.05,0:08:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}沒有逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而是 找更過分的結束方式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}拜託了 一生的懇求
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}此葉姊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}卑鄙啊 這麼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不都約定好別這麼說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.69,0:09:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因為一起做為高中生了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}以前像這樣拜託你的話你都會聽的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}才不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只是個人自言自語
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.60,0:09:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}大概我想那孩子只是不了解"理所當然"吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.46,0:09:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}非常簡單的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.22,0:09:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你聽到我的自言自語了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.10,0:09:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}聽到的話 就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.68,0:09:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這是她的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.35,0:09:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}罪和詛咒會怎麼樣的提示
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.45,0:09:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}簡單來說 就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.71,0:09:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我可沒從 春亮那得到答案喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.08,0:09:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那孩子跟我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.42,0:09:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我以前也想過同樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.89,0:09:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}現在的我仍然還是沒有找到解答
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.14,0:09:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是 我一直在春亮的家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:09:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.02,0:10:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}此葉姊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.50,0:10:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}悲鳴 哀傷的悲鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}滑稽的悲鳴 痛苦的悲鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}全部的悲鳴都令人懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是道具的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.92,0:10:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}曾是道具的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.87,0:10:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}被用 被雍有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}被需要的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}悲鳴 悲鳴……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.51,0:10:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}證明自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.43,0:10:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}煩死了 煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}住口 別叫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.10,0:10:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.90,0:11:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}菲雅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.02,0:11:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.30,0:11:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}菲雅 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.03,0:11:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}喂 菲雅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.64,0:11:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}煩死了 悲鳴就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這是 第十九號機關
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.55,0:11:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}掘式螺旋態 人體鑽孔機
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我 我的其中一個 使用了357次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}還是358次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}最後一個使用人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.14,0:11:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.57,0:11:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我是上野錐霞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.40,0:11:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}學校的班長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.95,0:11:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}住手 菲雅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.31,0:12:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}菲雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}果然還是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.05,0:12:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}菲…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.90,0:12:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怪物繃帶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}開什麼玩笑 幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}已經吸飽了 沒事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.51,0:12:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}傷口…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.48,0:13:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怪物繃帶是活著 所以會吸血
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}為了止住即將死亡的傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.44,0:13:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}會比死亡更痛的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.35,0:13:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這就是這繃帶的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.36,0:13:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你就是我的後援嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.93,0:13:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因為關係到生命 所以擅自動手了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.95,0:13:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}為什麼 擅自的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.69,0:13:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}還可以戰鬥 那個臭婊子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.52,0:13:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不管幾次都要打…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}後援為了讓前線的騎士完成使命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}會進行最大限度的支援
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.87,0:13:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}相信那是最佳的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}無謂的浪費生命 我也會被判斷成無能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.04,0:13:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}還以為是怎樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:14:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}打開遮蔽物 讓我看看臉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.75,0:14:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果是必須的話 那就
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}可惡 到底跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.82,0:14:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我看見菲雅了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在哪邊 現在在找他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.60,0:14:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}果然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.94,0:14:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}樣子有些奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.11,0:14:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就跟她說些話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.48,0:14:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這樣啊 接下來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.48,0:14:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不 沒有事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}現在她 有些不安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.06,0:14:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}大概 什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}班長 抱歉 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.08,0:14:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不 沒什麼大事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只是 不知如何說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.85,0:14:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}說實話 我很混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.01,0:14:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}看到不可思議的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.36,0:14:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}菲雅 菲雅手上的魔術方塊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}班長 抱歉 能先忘掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.27,0:14:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.32,0:15:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}後面會好好說明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.53,0:15:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.52,0:15:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你也有你的苦衷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.65,0:15:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.60,0:15:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}謝謝 班長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.92,0:15:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}證明我存在過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.30,0:15:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}地上滿是鮮血
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.11,0:15:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}被用水沖過的血
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.08,0:15:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}血流成河
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.72,0:15:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}然而 沖洗掉那些血的誰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.75,0:15:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不停的血
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.87,0:15:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}準備成為新血的誰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.81,0:15:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是 我喜歡他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只有他對我說出同情的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.90,0:15:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就算現在還記得 殘留於記憶中的悲鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.77,0:15:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}失去了誰 喜歡著的某人的悲鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那是我強迫著他發出的悲鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.19,0:16:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}開始的大海嗎 為什麼想起了從前的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是 開始已經結束了 這也不壞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.51,0:16:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}想起來吧 想起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.59,0:16:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她是什麼樣的人 在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.28,0:16:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}想起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.82,0:16:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}難道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}什麼嘛 比在電視上看到的更加恐怖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.42,0:16:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這可是全黑的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.16,0:16:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}無邊的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}簡直跟我以前待的地方一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是 為何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.51,0:16:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}會有留戀的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}菲雅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真是的 為何會如此留戀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.29,0:17:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我可是要殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.88,0:17:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他是不會過來追我的 這被詛咒的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}菲雅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}被詛咒的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.80,0:17:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}冰凍的 寒冷的 黑暗的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.21,0:17:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我只是回到只有我的地方而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.42,0:17:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是 比從前更加寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}重要的事情忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:18:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她非常的重 而且是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以躲起來的地方也沒想好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那麼 就去找她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.87,0:18:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}菲雅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}很溫暖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.75,0:18:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你醒過來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.89,0:18:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不過 怎麼說呢 跟你的體型不符合啊 超級重
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不要說我重 這是第二次了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.14,0:18:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}第一次是什麼時候 啊 你剛來的時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}對女士怎麼能說這麼無禮的話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.07,0:18:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真巧啊 我也很生氣 詛咒你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我再說一遍 詛咒你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我的詛咒很靈驗的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.77,0:18:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以 不想被詛咒的話就別說話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.91,0:19:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你說「放我下來」或者「別管我」的瞬間 你就會遇到不幸的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.98,0:19:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}會怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.69,0:19:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}胸部就不再長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.63,0:19:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.85,0:19:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}再說 你的詛咒對我是無效的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.88,0:19:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}沒用 沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因為沒用 所以我是不會放你下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}也不會聽你的任性要求
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.06,0:19:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就這樣把你帶回家裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.37,0:19:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}無論怎麼樣都會把你帶回去的 做好覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.28,0:19:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真囂張 明明只是個不知羞恥的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.30,0:19:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那可真抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.88,0:19:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}哦 怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.59,0:19:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}正好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.37,0:19:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就這樣聽我說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.26,0:19:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}說話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.89,0:19:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是的 不趁現在的話 我的決心就會動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.21,0:19:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}春亮 我害怕悲鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:19:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}正確來說 是害怕親近的人的悲鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.56,0:20:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}像今天這樣 你被別人傷害了而發出慘叫的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.73,0:20:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我又會回復自己的本性了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}要放手的話 就趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.42,0:20:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}為什麼說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.65,0:20:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我不知道我是否有留在這裡的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.46,0:20:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我是否擁有解除詛咒 失去罪孽的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.35,0:20:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那個 我不知道我有說過資格之類的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.64,0:20:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}想留的話留在這裡就行了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.15,0:20:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}重要的是你自己是否想留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.76,0:20:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}即使詛咒不了你 你也別小瞧我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.85,0:20:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我會讓你知道我能使用更直接的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.32,0:20:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怎麼樣 很冷吧 讓你好看的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.31,0:20:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這樣就給你施加了感冒的詛咒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.63,0:20:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那還真可怕啊 無論是誰每年都會中一次的詛咒
Comment: 0,0:21:11.81,0:21:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.51,0:22:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}哈啾 等等 菲雅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.10,0:22:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好了 你就老實待著吧 我不是說要給你擦背嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.33,0:22:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}別 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.65,0:22:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}別脫我衣服！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.62,0:22:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真的會感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.25,0:22:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.39,0:22:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你們在幹嘛 難得上野擔心你而特意跑過來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.58,0:22:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我真笨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.77,0:22:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}等等 這是誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.78,0:22:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}什麼誤會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.41,0:23:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}確實 這是第一次 不知道能不能做好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.22,0:23:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我會盡量用身體來侍奉你 會讓你很爽的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.67,0:23:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我不會再放任不管了 我也一起來幹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.94,0:23:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}第四章 夜晚是母親和抱枕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.00,0:23:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不看的話就詛咒你喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.19,0:23:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}
